WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Hi everyone, my name is Ryan Johnson and I'm a Data Science Advisor here at Posit.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:10.000
And I just want to take a few moments to talk about certain data science scenarios

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:13.000
where you may find Posit Connect to be particularly helpful.

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Now most data science teams aim to create insights that can drive a group, company, or industry forward.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:24.000
And maybe your group today is already using Posit Workbench to develop these insights,

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:29.000
including Shiny apps, fast APIs, Quarto documents, and much more.

00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:32.000
For our first scenario, have you ever been in a situation

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:37.000
where you needed to easily share insights with certain groups or individuals?

00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:41.000
Maybe your team has built an impressive Shiny application in R

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:44.000
and you tried to share it with others using email.

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:46.000
Well, your email probably looked like this,

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:53.000
where you tried your best to explain how viewers can install R, RStudio, packages, package versions,

00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:56.000
and get it running on their personal computers.

00:00:56.000 --> 00:00:59.000
Well, it would be much easier if instead you could provide viewers

00:00:59.000 --> 00:01:04.000
with a simple link to the Shiny application hosted on Posit Connect.

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:09.000
You might also need Posit Connect if you find that your day is full of recurring tasks

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:15.000
that you need to complete every hour, every day, every week, month, or even year.

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:18.000
And here are just some tasks that Posit Connect can help with.

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:23.000
Maybe you need to send a weekly report to your boss or update a machine learning model.

00:01:23.000 --> 00:01:28.000
Maybe you need to extract new data from an API and load that data into a database

00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:30.000
or any other recurring job.

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:36.000
For our third scenario, have you ever needed to simply give your data science insights a secure home?

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:39.000
Maybe you've had a conversation like this before with a colleague

00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:45.000
where someone wants to review a report, but your team can't remember where that report lives.

00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:49.000
With Posit Connect, you can now give those insights a home.

00:01:49.000 --> 00:01:53.000
For our fourth scenario, have you ever been in a situation where someone had access

00:01:53.000 --> 00:01:57.000
to a dashboard or report that they weren't supposed to see?

00:01:57.000 --> 00:02:01.000
With Posit Connect, you can easily control access to your data insights,

00:02:01.000 --> 00:02:05.000
especially if they contain sensitive information.

00:02:05.000 --> 00:02:10.000
For our last scenario, have you ever created a report, application, or dashboard

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:15.000
that underwent multiple revisions, and when it came down to sharing the final version,

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:18.000
you can't remember which version is the right one?

00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:23.000
With Posit Connect, you can publish different versions of the same asset to a single location

00:02:23.000 --> 00:02:27.000
and easily revert back to a previous version if needed.

00:02:27.000 --> 00:02:32.000
And those are my top five scenarios where Posit Connect can help your data science team.

00:02:32.000 --> 00:02:36.000
If you'd like to learn more about Posit Connect, feel free to reach out to us,

00:02:36.000 --> 00:02:38.000
and we'd love to chat more.

